<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasDataConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "LEGACY: Use :hasConstraint instead. Links an input requirement to a specific quality threshold that must be met by the data."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasDataConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "LEGADO: Use :hasConstraint en su lugar. Vincula un requisito de entrada con un umbral de calidad específico que deben cumplir los datos."@es .
