<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasDomainSector> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A sub-property of dcat:theme linking a resource to its domain sector.\n\nRECOMMENDED: Use EU Publications Office Data Theme NAL (DCAT-AP 3.0.1):\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/AGRI  # Agriculture\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENER  # Energy\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/HEAL  # Health\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN  # Transport\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI  # Environment\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH  # Science/Technology\n\nReference: http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasDomainSector> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una sub-propiedad de dcat:theme que vincula un recurso con su sector de dominio.\n\nRECOMENDADO: Usar EU Publications Office Data Theme NAL (DCAT-AP 3.0.1):\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/AGRI  # Agricultura\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENER  # Energía\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/HEAL  # Salud\n  http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN  # Transporte\n\nReferencia: http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasDomainSector> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has domain sector"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasDomainSector> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene sector de dominio"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasFeatureOfInterest
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasFeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasFeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasFeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a DataAsset, Metric, or DataSpecification to the entity or phenomenon it concerns (e.g., a specific crop or product). Used to define atomic semantic specifications."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasFeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Vincula un activo de datos, métrica o Perfil de Datos con la entidad o fenómeno sobre el que versa (p. ej., un cultivo específico). Se usa para definir especificaciones semánticas atómicas."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasFeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has feature of interest"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasFeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene característica de interés"@es .
