# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricStandard
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricStandard> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricStandard> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a metric or field-level value constraint to the standard or reference system used for its value. It can be a unit of measurement (QUDT) or a concept scheme/vocabulary (SKOS). Unifies the previous hasMetricUnit and usesVocabulary properties."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricStandard> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Vincula una métrica o perfil con el estándar o sistema de referencia utilizado para su valor. Puede ser una unidad de medida (QUDT) o un esquema de conceptos/vocabulario (SKOS). Unifica las propiedades anteriores hasMetricUnit y usesVocabulary."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricStandard> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has metric standard"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricStandard> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene estándar de métrica"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricUnit
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "DEPRECATED: Use :hasMetricStandard instead. The unit of measurement for the metric value referencing a URI (e.g., qudt:KiloGM, unit:PERCENT)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "OBSOLETO: Use :hasMetricStandard en su lugar. La unidad de medida para el valor de la métrica referenciando una URI (p. ej., qudt:KiloGM, unit:PERCENT)."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has metric unit (deprecated)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene unidad de métrica (obsoleto)"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasMetricUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#deprecated> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
