<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasObservableProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has observable property"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasObservableProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene propiedad observable"@es .
