# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/spatialGranularityConcept
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/spatialGranularityConcept> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/spatialGranularityConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/idsa/core/Resource> .
