<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/spatialGranularityConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a resource to a SKOS concept describing its spatial granularity.\n\nRECOMMENDED vocabularies (DCAT-AP 3.0.1):\n- EU NUTS: http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/nuts\n- INSPIRE Codelists: http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/codelist/\n- ISO 3166 (Countries): http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/country\n\nExamples: NUTS level 1 (country), NUTS level 2 (region), NUTS level 3 (province)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/spatialGranularityConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Vincula un recurso con un concepto SKOS que describe su granularidad espacial.\n\nVocabularios RECOMENDADOS (DCAT-AP 3.0.1):\n- EU NUTS: http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/nuts\n- INSPIRE Codelsits: http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/codelist/\n- ISO 3166 (Countries): http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/country\n\nEjemplos: NUTS nivel 1 (país), NUTS nivel 2 (región), NUTS nivel 3 (provincia)."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/spatialGranularityConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "granularidad espacial (concepto)"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/spatialGranularityConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "spatial granularity (concept)"@en .
