# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A grouping of multiple DataSpecifications. Useful to represent the set of variables that a dataset offers or an application requires."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una agrupación de múltiples DataSpecifications. Útil para representar el conjunto de variables que ofrece un dataset o requiere una aplicación."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Profile"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Perfil de Datos"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/idsa/core/DataRepresentation> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Physical representation of (structured) data. Specializes ids:DataRepresentation \n    from the IDSA taxonomy to add EDAAnOWL-specific semantics for data profiles and quality metrics.\n    \n    Alignment: ids:DataRepresentation extends dcat:Distribution (W3C DCAT 2+), \n    ensuring interoperability with DCAT-based catalogs while maintaining IDSA compliance."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Representación física de datos (estructurados). Especializa ids:DataRepresentation \n    de la taxonomía IDSA para añadir semántica específica de EDAAnOWL para perfiles de datos y métricas de calidad.\n    \n    Alineación: ids:DataRepresentation extiende dcat:Distribution (W3C DCAT 2+), \n    asegurando interoperabilidad con catálogos basados en DCAT mientras mantiene conformidad IDSA."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Representation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Representación de Datos"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification
