<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Standard> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid36 .
_:genid36 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onClass> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest> .
_:genid36 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#qualifiedCardinality> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger> .
_:genid36 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasFeatureOfInterest> .
_:genid36 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid37 .
_:genid37 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onClass> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty> .
_:genid37 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#qualifiedCardinality> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger> .
_:genid37 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasObservableProperty> .
_:genid37 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Atomic and reusable semantic unit that describes WHAT is being observed (Feature of Interest) and WHICH property is measured (Observable Property).\n    \nDataSpecifications are schema-agnostic. They do not contain mapping information (mapsField), units, or technical distribution details (resolutions, CRS), which belong to Distribution, FieldMapping, or explicit constraints."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Unidad semántica atómica y reutilizable que describe QUÉ se está observando (Feature of Interest), QUÉ propiedad se mide (Observable Property) y CÓMO se representa (Tipo de Dato, Estándar de Métrica).\n    \nLos DataSpecifications son ahora independientes del esquema. Ya no contienen información de mapeo (mapsField) ni detalles técnicos de la distribución (resoluciones, CRS), los cuales se han movido a Distribution o FieldMapping."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Specification"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Perfil de Datos"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/FeatureOfInterest> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "De lo que se habla o lo que se observa (el objeto real o fenómeno). Ejemplos: una naranja, una parcela, un lote de aceite. RECOMENDADO: Usar SIEX o AGROVOC para clasificar el tipo de objeto."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The phenomenon or entity being observed or described (the 'thing' itself). Examples: an orange, a plot of land, a batch of oil. RECOMMENDED: Use SIEX or AGROVOC to classify the object type."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Característica de Interés"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Feature of Interest"@en .
