<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FieldMapping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "La clase 'puente' que instancia un DataSpecification reutilizable para un campo específico en una distribución. Mapea el concepto semántico a un identificador físico (mapsField) y proporciona métricas de calidad específicas del campo."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FieldMapping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The 'bridge' class that instantiates a reusable DataSpecification for a specific field in a distribution. It maps the semantic concept to a physical identifier (mapsField) and carries field-level technical details such as unit, data type, observation metric, and quality metrics."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FieldMapping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Field Mapping"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FieldMapping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Vínculo de Perfil"@es .
