<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/SpatialTemporalAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/SpatialTemporalAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Subclase de DataAsset para datos con cobertura espacial y temporal, como datos de Observación de la Tierra."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/SpatialTemporalAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Subclass of DataAsset for data with spatial and temporal coverage, such as Earth Observation data."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/SpatialTemporalAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Activo Espacio-Temporal"@es .
