# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/VerifiableDataSpecification
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/VerifiableDataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/VerifiableDataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/VerifiableDataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A DataSpecification that is intended to be cryptographically verified. It should be linked to a Verifiable Credential using :hasCredential. This enables trusted quality assertions in data spaces by separating the profile metadata from its cryptographic proof."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/VerifiableDataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un DataSpecification destinado a ser verificado criptográficamente. Debe vincularse a una Credencial Verificable usando :hasCredential. Esto permite aserciones de calidad confiables en espacios de datos separando los metadatos del perfil de su prueba criptográfica."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/VerifiableDataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Perfil de Datos Verificable"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/VerifiableDataSpecification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Verifiable Data Specification"@en .
